--------------------------------------
TEMPLATE-GITHUB-ACTIONS-SEMVER-TAGGING 

Here is a simple example of using GitHub Actions to implement semantic versioning (semver). 
There are three files, each describing a slightly different workflow:

  - patch.yml: Triggered only from fixed branches (e.g., fix/1.0.x).
  - minor.yml: Triggered always.
  - major.yml: Triggered manually.

--------------------------------------
REPOSITORY STRUCTURE
.
├── .github
│   └── workflows
│       ├── patch.yml
|       ├── minor.yml
│       └── major.yml
└── README

--------------------------------------
REF:
  - alpine/semver: https://github.com/alpine-docker/semver
